Package: ErInjuryExplorer
Title: Shiny Explorer for NEISS Emergency Room Injury Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Chenguang",
             family = "Yang",
             email = "cyang314@ucr.edu",
             role = c("aut", "cre")))
Author: Chenguang Yang [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Chenguang Yang <cyang314@ucr.edu>
Description: Provides a Shiny application for exploring the emergency room
    injury data used in Chapter 4 of Mastering Shiny. The app summarizes patient
    demographics and injury variables, shows patient narratives by injured body
    part, and includes an extra product-code exploration tab.
